{{Quote|Without necessary capital powers it is considered impossible to maintain the stability of the New Order and the security of the greatest number of civilizations in the galaxy.|Capital Powers Act, Preface, Section II|<ref name="Children of the Jedi (novel)">[[Children of the Jedi (novel)|''Children of the Jedi'']]</ref>}}
The '''Capital Powers Act''' was an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] law that authorized the use of lethal forces against mutineers. The ''[[Eye of Palpatine]]'' was programmed with it.

